Description
-----------

This is software is an example of application v4l library to control pan/tilt
camera. Originaly it was intedted to work with Logitech Sphere camera however
it might work with other cameras that use the same control system. To run this
demo one should have OpenCV installed. The main file demenstrating how to use 
camera features is src/main.cpp.


Building
--------

Required libraries:
- OpenCV (libcv-dev)
- cmake  (cmake)

To compile type:

mkdir build
cd build
cmake .
make


Usage
-----

To run type:

./uvc4openCV

To control pan/tilt use arrows.

